  "V-VERSION": {
   "name": "V-VERSION",
   "file": "verbs.zil",
   "line": 348,
   "endLine": 378,
   "source": "<ROUTINE V-VERSION (\"AUX\" (CNT 17))\n\t <TELL D ,GAME\n\"|\nInfocom interactive fiction - a story of intrigue|\nCopyright (c) 1985 by Infocom, Inc.  All rights reserved.|\n\">\n\t ;<COND (<NOT <==? <BAND <GETB 0 1> 8> 0>>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"Licensed to Tandy Corporation.|\n\">)>\n\t <TELL\nD ,GAME \" is a trademark of Infocom, Inc.|\nRelease \">\n\t <PRINTN <BAND <GET 0 1> *3777*>>\n\t <TELL \" / Serial number \">\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t <COND (<G? <SET CNT <+ .CNT 1>> 23>\n\t\t\t<RETURN>)\n\t\t       (T\n\t\t\t<PRINTC <GETB 0 .CNT>>)>>\n\t <COND (<NOT <0? ,VARIATION>>\n\t\t<TELL \" / \">\n\t\t<COND (<EQUAL? ,VARIATION 1 2>\n\t\t       <TELL \"Traveler\">)\n\t\t      (T <TELL \"Spy\">)>\n\t\t<TELL \"'s viewpoint, \">\n\t\t<COND (<0? <MOD ,VARIATION 2>>\n\t\t       <TELL \"long\">)\n\t\t      (T <TELL \"short\">)>\n\t\t<TELL \" variation\">)>\n\t <CRLF>>"
  },
